        public int getWorldId()
        An identifier for the game world where the event takes place. Every event can happen in any game world. This just ties the current status for that event to a WorldName.

        public String getState()

        The current status of the event. The possible states are:

        • STATUS_ACTIVE
        • STATUS_FAIL
        • STATUS_INACTIVE
        • STATUS_PREPARATION
        • STATUS_SUCCESS
